      "schema_version": 1,
      "section": "Scope of Determinism",
      "status": "active",
      "supported_until": "2028-01-01",
      "title": "TDD and Determinism Policy",
      "type": "governance"
    },
    "text": "## Scope of Determinism\n\nThe following components are **determinism-critical** and require test coverage:\n\n| Component | Examples | Why Critical |\n|-----------|----------|--------------|\n| **Parsers** | YAML frontmatter, config loaders | Incorrect parsing corrupts downstream state |\n| **Generators** | Doc scaffolds, template renderers | Output drift breaks consumers |\n| **Metadata Engines** | standardize_metadata.py | Metadata is the source of truth |"
  },
